  "instructions": [
    "1. Heat butter in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "2. Add diced onion and cook for 3-4 minutes until translucent.",
    "3. Add minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "4. Add shrimp and cook for 2-3 minutes per side until pink and cooked through.",
    "5. In a small bowl, mix together spicy red pepper paste, salt, and black pepper.",
    "6. Add the mixture to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "7. Serve the shrimp mixture over torn dabo bread.",
    "8. Garnish with chopped cilantro and a squeeze of lemon juice.",
    "9. Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
